                        "text": "The gecko repulses the metal attached to its body in all directions, dealing 2d6 bludgeoning damage (DC 17 basic Reflex save) to all creatures in a 10-foot emanation. The gecko can't use Launch Metal again for 1d4 rounds."
                    }
